{"type":"message","id":"0604e051","parentId":"d0b217b1","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:38:31.887Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to execute a task from a cron configuration file related to real-time stock price monitoring. Let me first read the configuration file to understand what needs to be done.\n\nThe file path is: ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md\n\nLet me read this file first to understand the task requirements.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3badf0cd681842789ea960b5","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773110305719}}
{"type":"message","id":"b51a038c","parentId":"0604e051","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:38:31.898Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3badf0cd681842789ea960b5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 以下描述的文件都在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt；\n- 如果存在可用脚本，优先复用，不满足当前场景时才允许创建新脚本。\n- 执行时严格按照要求的文件名称及后缀，防止执行到不存在的文件。\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘，未收盘，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n2、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n3、阅读~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md内的skill使用说明，严格按照要求使用skill；\n4、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n5、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n6、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n7、读取receiver-list.txt接受者用户列表文件，使用命令openclaw message broadcast --channel feishu --account stock --targets <user_id1> --targets <user_id2>... --message <xxx>，\n   将预警数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给列表文件中的用户；\n   - --targets <user_id> 参数可重复\n8、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773110311896}}
{"type":"message","id":"afb821c9","parentId":"b51a038c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:38:42.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the task. Let me read the related files to understand the full requirements:\n1. TOOLS.md - for skill usage instructions\n2. get-data-template.md - for data format requirements\n3. alert-rules.md - for alert rules\n4. receiver-list.txt - for recipient list\n5. alert-template.md - for alert message format\n\nLet me read these files one by one.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e1b3d51e91184467866f3513","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/TOOLS.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_188596a966a241209be85b66","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d5ec3f22fa704d69a09b311a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8e52843705eb47689c537a08","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/receiver-list.txt"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e7be16d80cf44b98aa5f5710","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773110311899}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f85d3f7","parentId":"afb821c9","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:38:42.156Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e1b3d51e91184467866f3513","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/TOOLS.md'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/TOOLS.md'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773110322155}}
{"type":"message","id":"ab3f4183","parentId":"6f85d3f7","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:38:42.159Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_188596a966a241209be85b66","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773110322158}}
{"type":"message","id":"c2b3392c","parentId":"ab3f4183","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:38:42.163Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d5ec3f22fa704d69a09b311a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773110322161}}
{"type":"message","id":"73ebdb9a","parentId":"c2b3392c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:38:42.172Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8e52843705eb47689c537a08","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/receiver-list.txt'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/receiver-list.txt'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773110322171}}
{"type":"message","id":"a4d35ad0","parentId":"73ebdb9a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:38:42.175Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e7be16d80cf44b98aa5f5710","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773110322174}}
