{"type":"message","id":"49722cd3","parentId":"c9295436","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:39:20.215Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I now have a better understanding. Let me check if there's a receiver list somewhere and also check the filter script. Since there's no receiver-list.txt file, I need to find where the receivers are defined or create one. Let me also check the existing alert-data.txt which has some triggered alerts.\n\nLooking at the task requirements again:\n1. Check if market is open (using tushare-data skill)\n2. Clear realtime-data.txt if not empty\n3. Get real-time data per get-data-template.md format\n4. Filter based on alert-rules.md\n5. Send alerts via feishu to receivers from receiver-list.txt\n\nThe alert-rules.md says:\n- Generic: drop > 3% OR rise > 5% triggers\n- For 601857 (中国石油): rise > 2% OR drop > 1% triggers\n\nLooking at the existing realtime-data.txt, I can see some stocks already have data from 10:12. The current time is 10:38, so the market is open.\n\nSince there's no receiver-list.txt, let me check if there's another file or if I need to create one. Let me also look at existing scripts for reference on how to send alerts.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f6401499a6da46248aabbcb1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/send_alert.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e42022e1b81e41f897a036ce","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock -name \"*.txt\" | xargs grep -l \"user\" 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773110353563}}
{"type":"message","id":"fecef5ae","parentId":"49722cd3","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:39:20.221Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f6401499a6da46248aabbcb1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nSend stock alert via Feishu.\n\"\"\"\nimport requests\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# Read alert data\ndata_file = \"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt\"\nwith open(data_file, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    lines = [l.strip() for l in f.readlines() if l.strip()]\n\nif len(lines) <= 1:\n    print(\"No alert data to send.\")\n    exit(0)\n\n# Parse data\nheader = lines[0]\ndata_rows = lines[1:]\n\n# Build message content\nmessage = \"🚨 **股票预警通知**\\n\\n\"\nmessage += f\"⏰ 预警时间：{datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\\n\\n\"\nmessage += \"📊 **预警明细**\\n\\n\"\n\n# Create table\nmessage += \"| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 成交量 | 成交额 | 时间 |\\n\"\nmessage += \"|------|------|--------|--------|--------|--------|------|\\n\"\n\nfor row in data_rows:\n    parts = row.split('|')\n    if len(parts) >= 7:\n        code, name, price, change, volume, amount, time = parts[:7]\n        # Highlight abnormal changes\n        change_display = change\n        if change.startswith('+'):\n            change_display = f\"📈 {change}\"\n        else:\n            change_display = f\"📉 {change}\"\n        message += f\"| {code} | {name} | ¥{price} | {change_display} | {volume} | {amount} | {time} |\\n\"\n\nmessage += \"\\n⚙️ **预警规则**\\n\"\nmessage += \"• 📉 下跌 > 3% → 触发\\n\"\nmessage += \"• 📈 上涨 > 5% → 触发\\n\"\n\nprint(\"Message content:\")\nprint(message)\nprint(\"\\n---\")\nprint(f\"Sending to Feishu user: ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\")\n\n# Note: The actual Feishu send will be handled by OpenClaw message tool\n# This script just prepares the content\nprint(\"\\nMessage prepared successfully.\")\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773110360217}}
